### 알림 목록 조회 (최신순 페이징)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### SSE 스트림 연결
# EventSource 는 커스텀 헤더 불가 → token 쿼리 파라미터 사용
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/stream?token={{accessToken}}
Accept: text/event-stream

### 단건 읽음 처리
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 전체 읽음 처리
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 설정 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 설정 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticketOpenAlert": true,
  "gameStartAlert": true,
  "paymentAlert": true,
  "chatMentionAlert": false
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 채널 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 채널 등록 - 이메일
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelType": "EMAIL",
  "channelTarget": "test@example.com"
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 채널 등록 - Slack
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelType": "SLACK",
  "channelTarget": "#alerts"
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 채널 활성화/비활성화 토글
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/channels/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### 알림 채널 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/channels/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}
